'''普通濱蟹'''（[[學名|學名]]''Carcinus maenas''），又名'''美娜斯濱蟹'''或'''三葉真蟹'''，是[[濱海帶|濱海帶]]很普遍的[[蟹|蟹]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=100 of the World's Worst Invasive Alien Species|url=http://www.issg.org/database/species/search.asp?st=100ss&fr=1&sts=|publisher=Invasive Species Specialist Group|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-date=2015-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522083334/http://www.issg.org/database/species/search.asp?st=100ss&fr=1&sts=|dead-url=no}}</ref>它們原產於東北[[大西洋|大西洋]]及[[波羅的海|波羅的海]]，但進佔到相似環境的[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[南非|南非]]、[[南美洲|南美洲]]及[[北美洲|北美洲]]的大西洋和[[太平洋|太平洋]]海岸。它們闊9厘米，吃多種[[軟體動物|軟體動物]]、[[蠕蟲|蠕蟲]]及細小的[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]，對多種漁業潛藏影響。[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]][[物種存續委員會|物種存續委員會]]的入侵物種專家小組（ISSG）列為[[世界百大外來入侵種|世界百大外來入侵種]]。

==特徵==
[[File:Carcinus_maenas_-_Eemian_crab_borehole_Bergen_Netherlands.jpg|thumb]]發現屬於[[伊緬期|伊緬期]]的普通濱蟹[[化石|化石]]。]]
普通濱蟹的殼長達6厘米及闊9厘米<ref name="Yamada">{{cite journal en|journal=Journal of Shellfish Research |volume=20 |issue=3 |pages=905-9 |year=2001 |title=Field identification of the European green crab species: ''Carcinus maenas'' and ''Carcinus aestuarii'' |author=S. B. Yamada & L. Hauck |url=http://www.sgnis.org/publicat/papers/yamahauc.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927120719/http://www.sgnis.org/publicat/papers/yamahauc.pdf |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>，每隻[[眼睛|眼睛]]後沿邊有五隻短鋸齒，眼睛之間有三個起伏位置。這些起伏可以用來分辨普通濱蟹及[[艾氏濱蟹|艾氏濱蟹]]。艾氏濱蟹的甲殼沒有腫起的地方，並延伸至眼睛之前。另外，普通濱蟹的第一及第二游泳足是向外彎曲，艾氏濱蟹的則是筆直的。<ref name="Yamada"/>

普通濱蟹有很多不同顏色，由綠色至褐色、灰色或紅色。這些分別有遺傳的性質，但大部份都是環境因素所致。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Patterns of morphological and genetic variability in UK populations of the shore crab, ''Carcinus maenas'' Linnaeus, 1758 (Crustacea : Decapoda : Brachyura)|author=J. V. Brian, T. Fernandes, R. J. Ladle & P. A. Todd|year=2005|journal=Journal of Experimental Marine Biology|volume=329|issue=1|pages=47-54|doi=10.1016/j.jembe.2005.08.002}}</ref>那些脫殼較遲的會變成紅色，而非綠色。紅色的較為強壯及富攻擊性，但對環境（如[[鹽度|鹽度]]及[[缺氧|缺氧]]）的耐性較低。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=A. McKnight, L. M. Mathres, R. Avery & K. T. Lee|year=2000|title=Distribution is correlated with color phase in green crabs, ''Carcinus maenas'' (Linnaeus, 1758) in southern New England|journal=Crustaceana|volume=73|issue=6|pages=763-8|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/brill/cr/2002/00000075/00000005/art00004|doi=10.1163/156854000504787|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014054438/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/brill/cr/2002/00000075/00000005/art00004|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==原產及入侵地==
[[File:Carcinus_maenas_range.png|400px]]
普通濱蟹原產於[[歐洲|歐洲]]及[[北非|北非]]海岸，東至[[波羅的海|波羅的海]]，北至[[冰島|冰島]]及[[挪威|挪威]]中部，是分佈地內最為普遍的[[蟹|蟹]]。在[[地中海|地中海]]，它們被近親的[[艾氏濱蟹|艾氏濱蟹]]所驅逐。

普通濱蟹在[[北美洲|北美洲]]最先是於1817年的[[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]]發現，現已向南擴展至[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]南部。2007年，它們的分佈地已擴展至[[加拿大|加拿大]][[紐芬蘭-拉布拉多|紐芬蘭-拉布拉多]]的[[布雷森莎灣|布雷森莎灣]]（Placentia Bay）。<ref>{{cite web|title=A biological synopsis of the European green crab, ''Carcinus maenas'' |author=Greg Klassen and Andrea Locke |year=2007 |url=http://www.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/Library/330845.pdf |work=Canadian Manuscript Report of Fisheries and Aquatic Sciences No. 2818 |publisher=Fisheries and Oceans Canada |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100816203754/http://www.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/Library/330845.pdf |archivedate=2010-08-16 }}</ref>於1989年，它們出沒於[[舊金山灣|舊金山灣]]。它們於1997年、1998年及1999年分別抵達[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]、[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]及[[英屬哥倫比亞|英屬哥倫比亞]]<ref name="Alaska">{{cite web|url=http://www.pwsrcac.org/docs/d0015300.pdf |title=Non-indigenous aquatic species of concern for Alaska. Fact Sheet 1 |accessdate=2006-03-09 |format=PDF |author=Prince William Sound Regional Citizens' Advisory Council |year=2004 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060216193355/http://www.pwsrcac.org/docs/d0015300.pdf |archivedate=2006-02-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|author=E. D. Grosholz & G. M. Ruiz|year=1996|title=Predicting the impact of introduced marine species: Lessons from the multiple invasions of the European green crab ''Carcinus maenas''|journal=Biological Conservation|volume=78|issue=1-2|pages=59-66 |doi=10.1016/0006-3207(94)00018-2}}</ref>，10年內擴展達750公里。<ref name="European Green Crab Management">{{cite web|url=http://www.anstaskforce.gov/GreenCrabManagementPlan.pdf|title=Management plan for European Green Crab|author=Green Crab Control Committee|date=2002-11-13|publisher=United States Federal Aquatic Nuisance Species Task Force|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322091300/https://www.anstaskforce.gov/GreenCrabManagementPlan.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>到了2003年，它們更走到[[南美洲|南美洲]]的[[巴塔哥尼亞|巴塔哥尼亞]]。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=F. J. Hidalgo ''et al.''|year=2005|title=A prediction come true: the green crab invades the Patagonian coast |journal=Biological Invasions|volume=7|issue=3|pages=547-52|doi=10.1007/s10530-004-5452-3}}</ref>

在[[澳洲|澳洲]]，普通濱蟹首先於1800年代在[[維多利亞州|維多利亞州]][[菲利普港|菲利普港]]（Port Phillip）發現。自此它們散佈到東南及西南海岸，並於1971年、1976年及1993年分別到達[[新南威爾士|新南威爾士]]、[[南澳洲州|南澳洲州]]及[[塔斯曼尼亞|塔斯曼尼亞]]。於1965年在[[西澳州|西澳州]]發現一隻普通濱蟹，但卻自此沒有再發現其他。<ref name="Thresher">{{cite journal en|author=R. Thresher, C. Proctor, G. Ruiz, R. Gurney, C. MacKinnon, W. Walton, L. Rodriguez & N. Bax |year=2003 |title=Invasion dynamics of the European shore crab, ''Carcinus maenas'', in Australia |journal=Marine Biology |volume=142 |issue=5 |pages=867–76 |url=http://serc.si.edu/labs/marine_invasions/publications/PDF/Thresher_et_al_2003.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070612154900/http://www.serc.si.edu/labs/marine_invasions/publications/PDF/Thresher_et_al_2003.pdf |archivedate=2007-06-12 }}</ref>

普通濱蟹首次於1983年在[[南非|南非]]近[[開普敦|開普敦]]出現。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=P. J. Le Roux, G. M. Branch & M. A. P. Joska|year=1990|title=On the distribution, diet, and possible impact of the invasive European shore crab ''Carcinus maenas'' (L.) along the South African coast|journal=South African Journal of Marine Science|volume=9|issue=1|pages=85–93|doi=10.2989/025776190784378835}}</ref>自此它們擴散至北方的[[沙丹那灣|沙丹那灣]]（Saldanha Bay）及南方的[[坎普斯灣|坎普斯灣]]（Camps Bay）。

在[[巴西|巴西]]、[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]、[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]、[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]、[[紅海|紅海]]、[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]、[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]及[[緬甸|緬甸]]都有發現普通濱蟹。不過這些只是個別事件，並非入侵群落。[[日本|日本]]已被[[艾氏濱蟹|艾氏濱蟹]]或是艾氏濱蟹與普通濱蟹的[[混種|混種]]所入侵。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Episodic global dispersal in shallow water marine organisms: the case history of the European shore crabs ''Carcinus maenas'' and ''C. aestuarii''|year=2003|author=T. J. Carlton & A. N. Cohen|journal=Journal of Biogeography|volume=30|issue=12|pages=1809–20|url=http://www.sfei.org/bioinvasions/Reports/2003-GreenCrabDispersal383.pdf|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2699.2003.00962.x|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080829111536/http://www.sfei.org/bioinvasions/Reports/2003-GreenCrabDispersal383.pdf|archivedate=2008-08-29}}</ref>

根據[[生態|生態]]環境，相信普通濱蟹也會入侵到[[北美洲|北美洲]]由[[下加利福尼亞州|下加利福尼亞州]]至[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]的[[太平洋|太平洋]]海岸。<ref name="Alaska" />很多地方也有相類似的生態環境，現只有[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]並未大幅入侵。新西蘭政府已採取措施，如發出海生害蟲指引等來限制普通濱蟹的入侵。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.biosecurity.govt.nz/files/pests/european-shore-crab/european-shore-crab-guide.pdf|title=Marine Pest Guide|publisher=Biosecurity New Zealand|format=PDF|date=June 2006|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130218175719/http://www.biosecurity.govt.nz/files/pests/european-shore-crab/european-shore-crab-guide.pdf|archive-date=2013-02-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==生態==
[[File:Crab_Cangrexo_66eue.jpg|thumb]]
普通濱蟹可以在[[海洋|海洋]]及[[河口|河口]]環境生活，以泥、沙或岩石海床、水生[[植物|植物]]及[[沼澤|沼澤]]最為適合。它們可以抵受4-52‰的[[鹽度|鹽度]]，並能在0-30C的[[溫度|溫度]]下生存。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=A. N. Cohen & T. J. Carlton|year=1995|title=Introduction, dispersal and potential impacts of the green crab ''Carcinus maenas'' in San Francisco Bay, California|journal=Marine Biology|volume=122|issue=2|pages=225-37|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/p073572hgg1185ht/|doi=10.1007/BF00348935}}{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>故此它們可以在河口的低鹽度環境生存。使用[[細胞色素氧化酶|COI]][[基因|基因]]進行的[[分子生物學|分子生物學]]研究顯示在[[北海_(大西洋)|北海]]及[[比斯開灣|比斯開灣]]的群落互有遺傳的不同，而[[冰島|冰島]]及[[法羅群島|法羅群島]]的群落則有更大的不同。由此可見普通濱蟹很難進入較深的水域。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=J. Roman & S. R. Palumbi|title=A global invader at home: population structure of the green crab, ''Carcinus maenas'', in Europe|journal=Molecular Ecology|year=2004|volume=13|pages=2891-8|url=http://palumbi.stanford.edu/manuscripts/Roman%20and%20Palumbi%202004.pdf|doi=10.1111/j.1365-294X.2004.02255.x|format=PDF|pmid=15367106|issue=10|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070205201132/http://palumbi.stanford.edu/manuscripts/Roman%20and%20Palumbi%202004.pdf|archive-date=2007-02-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

雌蟹可以產達18萬5千顆卵，幼體會在離岸地方成長，當脫殼後幼蟹就會走到[[潮間帶|潮間帶]]。<ref name=USGS>{{cite web|author=Perry|url=http://nas.er.usgs.gov/queries/FactSheet.asp?SpeciesID=190|title=USGS Nonindigenous Aquatic Species Database|year=2005|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511141931/http://nas.er.usgs.gov/queries/FactSheet.asp?speciesID=190|archive-date=2009-05-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>幼蟹會生活在[[海藻|海藻]]及[[海草|海草]]之間，直至成為成體。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=B. Bedini|year=2002|title=Colour change and mimicry from juvenile to adult: ''Xantho poressa'' (Olivi, 1792) (Brachyura, Xanthidae) and ''Carcinus maenas'' (Linnaeus, 1758) (Brachyura, Portunidae)|journal=Crustaceana|volume=75|issue=5|pages=703-10|doi=10.1163/156854002760202688}}</ref>

普通濱蟹具有多種方式來將群落擴散<ref name=USGS/>，包括壓載水、船體、以海藻等物料包裝、泛舟、幼體隨海流遷徙等。在[[澳洲|澳洲]]的普通濱蟹可以擴散很長的距離，可以是由[[人類|人類]]活動所帶動。

普通濱蟹是多種[[生物|生物]]的[[掠食者|掠食者]]，尤其是[[雙殼綱|雙殼綱]]<ref>{{cite journal en|author=G. Miron ''et al.''|year=2005|title=Predation potential of the invasive green crab (''Carcinus maenas'') and other common predators on commercial bivalve species found on Prince Edward island|journal=Journal of Shellfish Research|volume=24|issue=2|pages=579–86|url=http://www.sgnis.org/publicat/papers/miroaude.pdf|format=PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927120800/http://www.sgnis.org/publicat/papers/miroaude.pdf|archivedate=2007-09-27}}</ref>、[[多毛類|多毛類]]及細小的[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wdfw.wa.gov/fish/ans/identify/html/index.php?species=carcinus_maenas |publisher=Washington Department of Fish and Wildlife |title=European green crab |accessdate=2010-02-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080613141700/http://wdfw.wa.gov/fish/ans/identify/html/index.php?species=carcinus_maenas |archivedate=2008-06-13 }}</ref>它們主要是夜間活動的，但隨潮汐也會在日間活動。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=M. Novak|year=2004|title=Diurnal activity in a group of Maine decapods|journal=Crustaceana|volume=77|issue=5|pages=603-20|doi=10.1163/1568540041717975|format=PDF}}</ref>在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]，它們掠食當地的[[蛤蜊|蛤蜊]]令其數量下降，並令入侵的蛤蜊（如[[寶石文蛤|寶石文蛤]]）增加。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=E. D. Grosholz|year=2005|title=Recent biological invasion may hasten invasional meltdown by accelerating historical introductions|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume=102|issue=4|pages=1088–91|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/102/4/1088|doi=10.1073/pnas.0308547102|pmid=15657121|pmc=545825|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-date=2008-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080523121559/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/102/4/1088|dead-url=no}}</ref>它們也導致了[[美國|美國]]東岸及[[加拿大|加拿大]][[砂海螂|砂海螂]]漁業的催毀，並令一些具重要商業價值的雙殼綱數量減少。<ref name=USGS/>它們也會吃[[魚類|魚類]]，但對[[美洲擬鰈|美洲擬鰈]]的影響卻很少。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=D. L. Taylor|year=2005|title=Predatory impact of the green crab (''Carcinus maenas'' Linnaeus) on post-settlement winter flounder (''Pseudopleuronectes americanus'' Walbaum) as revealed by immunological dietary analysis|journal=Journal of Experimental Marine Biology and Ecology|volume=324|issue=2|pages=112–26|doi=10.1016/j.jembe.2005.04.014}}</ref>它們會掠食幼少的[[牡蠣|牡蠣]]及[[首長黃道蟹|首長黃道蟹]]等[[物種|物種]]，或與之競爭資源，令當地的休閒垂釣也受到影響。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=K. D. Lafferty & K. D. Kuris|year=1996|title=Biological control of marine pests|journal=Ecology|volume=77|pages=1989–2000|url=http://www.jstor.org/pss/2265695|doi=10.2307/2265695|issue=7|jstor=10.2307/2265695|publisher=Ecological Society of America }}</ref>

==控制==
[[File:Cancer_productus.jpg|thumb]]在部份[[北美洲|北美洲]]地區可以限制普通濱蟹的擴散。]]
由於普通濱蟹對[[生態系統|生態系統]]造成的破壞，[[世界|世界]]各地就採取了控制入侵普通濱蟹的措施。在[[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]][[埃德加敦_(馬薩諸塞州)|埃德加敦]]，1995年為了保護當地的[[貝類|貝類]]，为捕捉普通濱蟹提供獎償，捕捉達10噸之多。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marine.csiro.au/crimp/nimpis/controlDetail.asp?ID=66 |author=F. R. McEnnulty, T. E. Jones & N. J. Bax |title=The Web-Based Rapid Response Toolbox. Web publication |accessdate=2006-03-09 |year=2002 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060519191846/http://www.marine.csiro.au/crimp/nimpis/controlDetail.asp?ID=66 |archivedate=2006-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

[[北美洲|北美洲]]東部的[[藍蟹|藍蟹]]能夠控制普通濱蟹的群落。這兩個[[物種|物種]]的數量是負相關的，[[切薩皮克灣|切薩皮克灣]]並沒有普通濱蟹，但藍蟹的數量卻很豐富。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=C. E. DeRivera, G. M. Ruiz, A. H. Hines & P. Jivoff |year=2005 |title=Biotic resistance to invasion: Native predator limits abundance and distribution of an introduced crab |journal=Ecology |volume=86 |issue=12 |pages=3367-76 |url=http://serc.si.edu/labs/marine_invasions/publications/PDF/DeRivera_et_al_%202005%20_Biotic_%20resistance_to_Green_Crab.pdf |format=PDF |doi=10.1890/05-0479 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610025151/http://www.serc.si.edu/labs/marine_invasions/publications/PDF/DeRivera_et_al_%202005%20_Biotic_%20resistance_to_Green_Crab.pdf |archivedate=2010-06-10 }}</ref>在北美洲西岸，普通濱蟹因受到當地''Romaleon antennarium''及[[紅黃道蟹|紅黃道蟹]]的掠食及與[[黃色食草蟹|黃色食草蟹]]的競爭而受限於上[[河口|河口]]。<ref>{{cite book en|author=S. B. Yamada|title=Global invader: the European Green Crab|year=2001|publisher=Oregon Sea Grant|id=ISBN 1-881826-24-4|pages=123}}</ref>就[[蟹奴屬|蟹奴屬]]''Sacculina carcini''的宿主特異性測試發現它們可以是普通濱蟹的生物防治。<ref name="Goddard">{{cite journal en|author=J. H. R. Goddard, M. E. Torchin, A. M. Kuris & K. D. Lafferty|year=2005|title=Host specificity of ''Sacculina carcini'', a potential biological control agent of introduced European green crab ''Carcinus maenas'' in California|journal=Biological Invasions|volume=7|issue=6|pages=895-912|url=http://www.werc.usgs.gov/chis/Goddardetal05.pdf|doi=10.1007/s10530-003-2981-0|format=PDF|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808075542/https://www.werc.usgs.gov/chis/Goddardetal05.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>蟹奴屬會選擇、感染及殺死原產於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]的[[蟹|蟹]]，包括[[首長黃道蟹|首長黃道蟹]]、[[紫色食草蟹|紫色食草蟹]]、黃色食草蟹及[[粗腿厚紋蟹|粗腿厚紋蟹]]。故此若使用蟹奴屬對付普通濱蟹，也會對當地的其他生物造成影響。<ref name="Goddard"/>

==漁業==
普通濱蟹在東北[[大西洋|大西洋]]有少量的漁業，每年漁獲約有1200噸，大部份都是在[[法國|法國]]及[[英國|英國]]。在西北大西洋，它們於1960年代是漁業的目標，及後自1996年，每年就有漁獲86噸。<ref>{{cite web|title=FAO Nominal Catches: ''Carcinus maenas''|url=http://www.fishbase.org/report/FAO/FAOCatchList.cfm?&scientific=Carcinus%20maenas|publisher=FishBase|access-date=2010-06-19|archive-date=2010-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100808055225/http://www.fishbase.org/report/FAO/FAOCatchList.cfm?&scientific=Carcinus%20maenas|dead-url=no}}</ref>

